Based on Airmaster’s proven Heavy Duty Air Circulator design, the High Ambient version is specially designed for the rigors of continuous operation in areas where the air temperature may be more than 104 degrees F (40 degrees C). While it is possible to operate a standard unit in ambient temperatures greater than 104 F, for each 18 degrees F increase above, the life of the motor is reduced by 50%. The High Ambient HD Air Circulator is designed to provide full service life up to 150 degrees F (65 degrees C). Unit is designed for use in:

  • Laundries
  • Foundries
  • Brick Making
  • Glass Factories
  • And anywhere high ambient temperatures are found
